'''Maze-stalk''' was the primary crop grown on [[Aduba-3/Legends|Aduba-3]]. It was a tall [[Grass/Legends|grass]] which annually bore a red melon-like [[Fruit/Legends|fruit]]. The husks could be used to make cloth.

It was brought to the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] by [[Sacred Way/Legends|Sacred Way]] colonists. Since it did not have the protective thorns that graced plants native to Aduba-3, it was highly susceptible to being eaten by animals, including [[high-hound]]s.

